5. The system of claim 4, wherein the plurality of medical predictions (d) comprising a set of prescriptions for medication and diagnostic test.

6. The system of claim 4, wherein the structured reasoning (t) comprising at least one of (i) intermediate hypotheses and their supporting evidence, (ii) motivations for diagnostic test orders, and (iii) discarded hypotheses with rationales from one or more doctor agents.
